ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of KIRSTINE STEWART of Los Angeles, California, United States of America, to be a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the National Museum of Science and Technology, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of E. Virginia I. McLaughlin, whose term has expired.
